{"tid":985460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<蘋果> 如果林鄭係雞，羅致光就係豉油","createTime":"2019-01-17T15:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T06:46:45.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d623343c7822017b1a4ebbf07ea0853940b0f34","tid":985460,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:04:14.000Z","msg":"如果林鄭係雞，羅致光就係豉油 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n2019-01-17<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n如果人有120歲，60歲只係中年。<br />\n<br />\n如果羅致光係人，香港就係天堂。<br />\n<br />\n如果長者要重新定義，89歲才有投票權。<br />\n<br />\n如果有奶便是娘，高呼「X你老母」的黑警唔使交水費。<br />\n<br />\n如果野豬摷垃圾桶係死罪，狼吞了五千萬落肚，屬財技，融資之嘛。<br />\n<br />\n如果林鄭係上帝感召，香港人就係邪靈劈友。<br />\n<br />\n如果個個61歲都想做特首，淘寶就發大財了。<br />\n<br />\n如果台灣被順豐速遞，香港一國兩制個郵包，早已空運上火星。<br />\n<br />\n如果明日大嶼係點心紙，電騙黨收線，轉場去茶樓吃大茶飯。<br />\n<br />\n如果粉嶺高球場=運動，白襪仔就=黃背心。<br />\n<br />\n如果鄭若驊大義滅親，佢老公一視同仁拎到綜援。<br />\n<br />\n如果習大大120歲，61歲的林鄭有機會忘年戀。<br />\n<br />\n如果林鄭120歲，記得幫羅致光BB換片，臭啊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190117/20592522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592522&d=IXeaUj7MBsH%2FpAjUoWaQHL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=e8bc4be1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F20592522&h=e0590ba1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20190117/20592522</a>"},{"pid":"99bdf2c0fe767823aa122b5b28de2b5960a5b3e3","tid":985460,"uid":58796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:19:57.000Z","msg":"如果林鄭係雞,佢唔拎老人綜援應該會餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14527c7347c956ecc17718a5443dfecff5b6990e","tid":985460,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"個標題<img src=\"/assets/